    public abstract class JsonrpcRequest
extends AbstractJsonrpcRequest
    Represents a JSON-RPC Request. 
     {
   "jsonrpc": "2.0",
   "id": "UUID",
   "method": string,
   "params": {},
   "timeout"?: number, defaults to 60 seconds; negative or zero to disable timeout
 }
    See Also:
    JSON-RPC specification
